# School Management Database

A simple C++ project implementing a school management database using SQLite. This project demonstrates basic database operations such as creating tables, inserting records, and querying student data.

## Features

- Add, update, and manage student records
- SQLite database integration
- Cross-platform build using CMake
- Modular design with separate database and student classes

## Prerequisites

- C++ compiler (C++11 or higher)
- [SQLite](https://www.sqlite.org/index.html)
- [CMake](https://cmake.org/)

## Getting Started

1. **Clone the repository**

```bash
git clone https://github.com/Bista-byte/School_management_database.git
cd School_management_database
```
